longBusinessSummary.0: Suprajit Engineering Limited manufactures, sells, and exports automotive cables and halogen lamps to original equipment manufacturers in India, the United States, the United Kingdom, Germany, and Luxembourg. It provides gear box, braking system, throttle controls, linear actuation, display cluster and telematics, gear shifter systems, control cables, lighting systems, friction products, and USB charging modules. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
